---
By: Ralph W. Trine
Locus:
  Page: 455
  Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Suffering
---
All the frictions, all the uncertainties, all the ills, the sufferings, the
fears, the forebodings, the perplexities of life come to us because we are
out of harmony with the divine order of things. ...So long as there is a
violation of laws, so long disease and suffering will result.
